<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٨٦٦ - د هـ د ي]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>دهدى يُدهْدِي، دَهْدِ، دَهْداةً ودَهْداءً، فهو مُدَهْدٍ، والمفعول مُدَهْدًى<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• دهدى الحجرَ:</span> دَحْرَجَه.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• دهدى الشَّيءَ:</span> قلَب بعضَه على بعض.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>